translations: 酒窝；球表面凹痕；涟漪（dimple 的复数）
现出酒窝；起涟漪（dimple 的第三人称单数）

sentences.sentence: Bess spoke up, smiling so that her dimples showed.
sentences.translation: 贝丝大声发言，微笑着，使脸上露出了两个酒窝。

sentences.sentence: Why do golf balls have dimples?
sentences.translation: 为什么高尔夫球上有“酒窝”？

sentences.sentence: She has two dimples on her face.
